      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GUSMAO (2) finished second two runs back at this track then improved last time out to score by a head over 1498m at this track. Well placed and there is no reason he cannot score again. FOOTPRINTS (3) was in the placings here last time at this track and drops in the weights. Wesley Cave who has two wins when partnering stays on. Best form puts her right in this. JOHNNY THE JET (6) failed to fire a shot last start at Murray Bridge but was responsible for two much better efforts prior, including a dominant maiden win here two back. Can bounce back sharply this time. FOX DUNNETT (7) went back early from his wide draw over 1498m at this track last time but hit the line strongly to finish fourth. Well placed and is among the chances. TAIPAN TOMMY (5) turned things around last start and scored by half a length over 1450m at Tennant Creek. Solid top-three prospects.",
